	* tcpd/libcouriertls.c (tls_create): Default TLS_PROTOCOL=SSL23,
	TLS_CIPHER_LIST=SSLv3:TLSv1:!SSLv2:HIGH:!LOW:!MEDIUM:!EXP:!NULL@STRENGTH

