2002-02-25  Mr. Sam  <mrsam@courier-mta.com>

	* imap/imapd.c: fix GETQUOTAROOT response

	* imap/testsuite: dump imapd output to a file instead of /dev/null,
	BSD's fcntl(O_NONBLOCK) chokes on /dev/null.

