	* imapscanclient.c: fix UIDNEXT in the STATUS response to take into
	account new mail.

2002-02-20  Mr. Sam  <mrsam@courier-mta.com>

	* couriertls, imapd: set socket into non-blocking mode, to correctly
	implement POSIX select() semantics.

